  "data": [
    {
      "title": "Windows安装virtualbox增强功能全屏化显示",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "context": "在Windows上通过Virtualbox安装deepin后，需安装增强工具实现全屏显示，点击安装时可能出现无法加载VBoxGuestAdditions.iso的提示。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "在Windows上用Virtualbox安装deepin后，为什么要安装增强工具？",
              "id": "5-479-1",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "实现deepin在virtualbox中全屏显示",
                  "answer_start": 36
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "安装增强工具时可能出现什么问题？",
              "id": "5-479-2",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "未能加载虚拟光盘C:\\Program Files\\Oracle\\VirtualBox\\VBoxGuestAdditions.iso到虚拟电脑Deepin.",
                  "answer_start": 70
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "安装增强功能第一步：检查VBox目录中是否有VBoxGuestAdditions.iso，官网下载的VBox通常有，需找到其中的VBoxLinuxAdditions.run。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "安装增强功能的第一步是什么？",
              "id": "5-479-3",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "检查VBox的目录中有无增强工具的镜像文件（VBoxGuestAdditions.iso）",
                  "answer_start": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "VBoxGuestAdditions.iso中哪个是安装增强的关键运行文件？",
              "id": "5-479-4",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "VBoxLinuxAdditions.run",
                  "answer_start": 85
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "在deepin中，可通过文件管理器查看相关文件，用ctrl+alt+t打开终端，运行sudo ./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run，重启后实现全屏。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "在deepin中如何打开终端？",
              "id": "5-479-5",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "<kbd>ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>alt</kbd>+<kbd>t</kbd>",
                  "answer_start": 42
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "在终端中运行什么命令可安装增强功能？",
              "id": "5-479-6",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "sudo ./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run",
                  "answer_start": 66
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "运行安装命令后需要做什么才能实现全屏？",
              "id": "5-479-7",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "重启virtualbox中的deepin系统",
                  "answer_start": 99
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "不懂命令行的用户，可在deepin的media文件夹-用户名文件夹中找到VBox_GAs_6.0.10，右击在终端中打开，输入sudo ./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run并重启。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "不懂命令行的用户在哪里能找到VBox_GAs_6.0.10？",
              "id": "5-479-8",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "deepin的系统盘中的media文件夹—用户名文件夹",
                  "answer_start": 24
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "不懂命令行的用户找到VBox_GAs_6.0.10后如何操作？",
              "id": "5-479-9",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "右击在终端中打开，输入sudo ./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run，回车，运行完成重启",
                  "answer_start": 75
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}